Introduction 
Welcome to the official development documentation for KSE. This project is a full breakdown of how the game is being created, from the first ideas to the final build. The goal is to give a clear look at what the game engine is, how it works, and what you can expect as it evolves. 
What KSE Is 
KSE is a 2D/3D game engine that will allow you to create games, such as fast paced video games. Hopefully this allows people to create games without the restriction of commercial expectations to learn everything at once.
What You Can Expect from This Document 
Throughout these pages, you’ll find: 
An overview of the software concept and design 
Details on how the systems are built 
Explanations of the coding process 
Notes on security, data handling, and online features 
Visuals, prototypes, and development updates 
Logic Visual maps
This document is designed to guide you through the creation of the project and show the work behind the final product. It’s not a tutorial — it’s a behind-the-scenes look at how KSE is being developed. 


